Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpAs a Senator, Harris was ranked the #1 most far-left Democrat in the entire Senate. She makes Bernie look like a moderate. She supports...🚩 Free government healthcare for illegal aliens🚩 Abolishing ICE🚩 Decriminalizing illegal immigration🚩 Mass amnesty for illegals🚩 Banning fracking🚩 Outlawing private health insurance🚩 Defunding the police🚩 Forcibly ripping guns out of the hands of law-abiding citizens...and as Vice President, she even cast the tie-breaking vote to cut Medicare by $237 billion dollars.
